  "instructions": [
    "Heat the butter in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the sliced Andouille sausage and cook until it is browned.",
    "Add the uncooked white rice and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken broth, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving."
